import Vue from 'vue'
import VueRouter from 'vue-router'
import UserVue from '@/components/user.vue'
import AuthorityVue from './components/authority.vue'
import ItemsVue from '../../shoppingcar/src/components/Item.vue'
import OrdersVue from './components/orders.vue'
import SystemVue from './components/system.vue'
Vue.use(VueRouter)

const router = new VueRouter({
  routes: [
    { path: '/', redirect: '/user' },
    { path: '/user', component: UserVue },
    { path: '/authority', component: AuthorityVue },
    { path: '/items', component: ItemsVue },
    { path: '/order', component: OrdersVue },
    { path: '/system', component: SystemVue },
  ],
})

export default router
